embed.description: Three regional champions and the defending World Champions will battle it out at the Worlds Semifinals in Madrid. The weekend begins with the two LPL teams, FunPlus Phoenix and Invictus Gaming facing off on November 2, 12PM CET / 4AM PDT. Day 2 continues with a Semifinals match between the LCK's SK Telecom T1 and the LEC's G2 Esports.
